keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
unmap <a-f>
map af LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
map s LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map R LinkHints.activateMode action=hover
map C LinkHints.activateMode action=focus
map yC LinkHints.activateMode action=copy-text
map <a-ƒ> LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map l scrollDown
map , previousTab
map . nextTab
map < closeTabsOnLeft
map > closeTabsOnRight
map u scrollFullPageUp
map <space> scrollFullPageDown
map h firstTab
map ' lastTab
map j goBack
map ; goForward
map [ goPrevious
map ] goNext
searchEngines:
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
y: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
